Zinc: This essential mineral is important for testosterone production and overall reproductive health. Zinc also supports immune function and helps maintain energy levels.




Maca Root: Known for its adaptogenic properties, Maca Root helps improve libido and sexual performance by balancing hormones and reducing stress levels.
